## 📊 Admin Dashboard — Complete Tab Guide

### 🛡️ Super Admin (All Tabs)

| Tab | What It Does |
|---|---|
| 📊 **Overview** | Charts: queries by category, confidence health, AI layer status |
| 📋 **Logs** | Full query log table — every user question and AI response |
| 🧠 **Knowledge** | Upload structured knowledge CSV/Excel files per university |
| 📱 **Dynamic CMS** | CRUD manager for all university content sections |
| 🛡️ **Approvals** | Queue of all pending/pending_delete entries across all universities |
| 👥 **Users** | Full user directory. Create University Admins. Assign, activate, deactivate, delete |
| 🏫 **Partner Approval** | User-submitted university requests — approve to create the university |
| 📂 **Data Files** | View uploaded files, delete all entries for a university |
| 👍 **Feedback** | User thumbs up/down ratings on chatbot answers |

### 🏫 University Admin (Restricted Tabs)
Sees: Overview, Logs, Knowledge, Dynamic CMS, Data Files, Feedback — **only for their assigned university**.

