## 📱 Dynamic CMS — Section System

The CMS supports **unlimited sections** for each university. Current built-in sections include:

| Section | Description |
|---|---|
| Emergency Contacts | Police, ambulance, campus security, wardens |
| Admissions | Eligibility, dates, process, documents |
| Courses | Programs offered, duration, credits |
| Fee Structure | Tuition, hostel, mess, exam fees |
| Scholarships | Merit, government, sports-based |
| Hostel Information | Blocks, rules, facilities |
| Placements | Top recruiters, average packages, stats |
| Faculty | Department-wise faculty listings |
| Events | Fests, seminars, deadlines |
| Notices | Official university announcements |

Each entry has: `title`, `content`, `priority`, `metadata (key-value)`, `status`, `created_by`, `version`.

> [!TIP]
> New sections can be added at runtime from the Admin Dashboard without any code changes.

